## 8. ✅ Final Security Checklist

- ✅ No secrets hardcoded in any source file
- ✅ `.env` in `.gitignore` — confirmed not committed
- ✅ Passwords hashed with BCrypt
- ✅ JWT required on all protected endpoints
- ✅ RBAC enforced — ADMIN / MANAGER / VIEWER
- ✅ `@PreAuthorize` used on sensitive endpoints
- ✅ Input validation on all POST/PUT (`@Valid`)
- ✅ Soft delete — no permanent data loss
- ✅ Error responses never expose stack traces
- ✅ SQL injection blocked — JPA parameterized queries
- ✅ Prompt injection rejected — AI middleware returns 400
- ✅ Rate limiting on AI service (flask-limiter)
- ✅ Security headers present (verified by ZAP re-scan)
- ✅ Zero Critical/High ZAP findings after Day 12
- ✅ PII audit passed — no personal data in prompts/logs
- ✅ Redis AI cache uses SHA256 key
- ⏳ JWT → `httpOnly` cookie (post-sprint)
- ⏳ Spring Boot rate limiting (post-sprint)

